{"tid":1630801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"環球時報指蘋果上架應用程式被亂港暴徒使用躲避警員","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:49:58.000Z","uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d2e3c21c48ddb5006de678d2235cffda9027651c","tid":1630801,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:02.000Z","msg":"等睇基佬爛果跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />基佬奶到雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地《環球時報》引述美國《彭博》報道，美國蘋果公司近日決定，重新上架一款香港地圖應用程式，是一個網站的手機版，能即時顯示香港警員所在的區域。報道說這個應用程式名為「HKmap.live」，被「亂港暴徒」廣泛使用，躲避警員逮捕。報道又說蘋果公司在本月初，曾拒絕該應用程式上架，理由是會「鼓動非法行為」，但日前改變主意，批准在香港的蘋果應用商店上架。報道形容這個應用程式是「亂港暴徒」通報警方資訊，令他們逃避法律制裁的「幫兇」，又說蘋果改變之前的正確決定，允許上架，令人十分費解。<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-06 21:31:46<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484644-20191006.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484644-20191006.htm&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6gWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=0daaec13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484644-20191006.htm&h=a2045b9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484644-20191006.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ec49f699f038f258b6319a15f6a9778534c3b5f0","tid":1630801,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆